{"image_id": "KMB_2010_page_25", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "PART II", "bbox": [162.5, 158.9, 240.5, 179.7]}, {"text": "(Continued)", "bbox": [162.5, 184.1, 263.2, 204.9]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [204.2, 242.4, 211.5, 263.2]}, {"text": "Operating profit for K-C Professional & Other products increased 0.9 percent as higher net selling", "bbox": [237.5, 242.4, 1112.3, 263.2]}, {"text": "prices and cost savings were mostly offset by inflation in key input costs and unfavorable currency", "bbox": [237.5, 267.4, 1112.4, 288.2]}, {"text": "effects.", "bbox": [237.5, 292.4, 298.2, 313.2]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [204.2, 331.5, 211.5, 352.3]}, {"text": "Operating profit for the health care segment decreased 28.7 percent. The benefit of higher sales volumes", "bbox": [237.5, 331.5, 1112.4, 352.3]}, {"text": "and cost savings were more than offset by higher selling and general expenses, including ongoing", "bbox": [237.5, 356.5, 1112.5, 377.3]}, {"text": "I-Flow litigation-related expenses, inflation in key cost inputs and lower net selling prices.", "bbox": [237.5, 381.5, 992.4, 402.3]}, {"text": "Organization Optimization Initiative", "bbox": [183.3, 448.5, 489.2, 469.4]}, {"text": "In June 2009, we announced actions to reduce our worldwide salaried workforce by approximately 1,600", "bbox": [204.2, 487.8, 1112.5, 508.7]}, {"text": "positions. These actions resulted in cumulative pretax charges of approximately $128 million in 2009. Related", "bbox": [162.5, 512.8, 1112.4, 533.7]}, {"text": "savings from this initiative were approximately $80 million in 2010 and $55 million in 2009. See Item 8, Note 5", "bbox": [162.5, 537.8, 1112.5, 558.7]}, {"text": "to the Consolidated Financial Statements for detail on costs incurred for the initiative.", "bbox": [162.5, 562.8, 878.5, 583.7]}, {"text": "Other (income) and expense, net", "bbox": [183.3, 629.9, 454.9, 650.7]}, {"text": "Other (income) and expense, net for 2010 includes a $79 million charge related to the adoption of highly", "bbox": [204.2, 669.2, 1112.4, 690.0]}, {"text": "inflationary accounting in Venezuela. In addition, Other (income) and expense, net includes currency transaction", "bbox": [162.5, 694.2, 1112.3, 715.0]}, {"text": "losses of $20 million in 2010 and $110 million in 2009. Included in 2009 was approximately $73 million of", "bbox": [162.5, 719.2, 1112.5, 740.0]}, {"text": "currency transaction losses related to operations in Venezuela.", "bbox": [162.5, 744.2, 683.0, 765.0]}, {"text": "Commentary:", "bbox": [183.3, 811.3, 297.9, 832.1]}, {"text": "2009 versus 2008", "bbox": [204.2, 850.3, 351.3, 871.2]}, {"text": "Percentage Change in Operating Profit Versus Prior Year", "bbox": [632.4, 898.4, 1045.5, 915.1]}, {"text": "Change Due To", "bbox": [821.1, 923.4, 932.4, 940.1]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [573.9, 965.1, 611.8, 981.8]}, {"text": "Change", "bbox": [565.5, 981.8, 620.2, 998.4]}, {"text": "Volume", "bbox": [641.0, 981.8, 696.6, 998.4]}, {"text": "Net", "bbox": [723.3, 965.1, 748.3, 981.8]}, {"text": "Price", "bbox": [717.4, 981.8, 754.4, 998.4]}, {"text": "Input", "bbox": [781.0, 965.1, 820.9, 981.8]}, {"text": "Costs(a)", "bbox": [775.2, 981.8, 826.7, 998.4]}, {"text": "Production", "bbox": [857.2, 948.4, 936.8, 965.1]}, {"text": "(Curtailment)/", "bbox": [845.3, 965.1, 949.0, 981.8]}, {"text": "Efficiencies", "bbox": [856.4, 981.8, 937.8, 998.4]}, {"text": "Currency", "bbox": [967.3, 981.8, 1035.8, 998.4]}, {"text": "Other(b)", "bbox": [1056.7, 981.8, 1112.4, 998.4]}, {"text": "Consolidated . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 1012.1, 544.7, 1032.9]}, {"text": "10.9", "bbox": [574.7, 1012.1, 611.1, 1032.9]}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [665.3, 1012.1, 689.6, 1032.9]}, {"text": "29", "bbox": [725.5, 1012.1, 746.4, 1032.9]}, {"text": "26", "bbox": [790.6, 1012.1, 811.5, 1032.9]}, {"text": "(5)", "bbox": [893.5, 1012.1, 917.8, 1032.9]}, {"text": "(14)", "bbox": [987.7, 1012.1, 1022.4, 1032.9]}, {"text": "(23)(c)", 