(4)", "bbox": [998.1, 1112.1, 1022.4, 1132.9]}, {"text": "(22)", "bbox": [1070.7, 1112.1, 1105.4, 1132.9]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [162.5, 1152.8, 181.0, 1169.4]}, {"text": "Includes raw materials deflation and energy and distribution variations.", "bbox": [195.8, 1152.8, 670.3, 1169.4]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [162.5, 1187.7, 181.9, 1204.3]}, {"text": "Includes organization optimization severance and related charges and cost savings.", "bbox": [195.8, 1187.7, 747.5, 1204.3]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [162.5, 1222.6, 181.0, 1239.2]}, {"text": "Strategic cost reduction charges of $60 million were included in 2008.", "bbox": [195.8, 1222.6, 663.9, 1239.2]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [204.2, 1258.4, 211.5, 1279.3]}, {"text": "Consolidated operating profit increased $278 million or 10.9 percent from the prior year. The benefits of", "bbox": [237.5, 1258.4, 1112.5, 1279.3]}, {"text": "higher net selling prices, cost savings of about $240 million and deflation in key cost components", "bbox": [237.5, 1283.4, 1112.4, 1304.3]}, {"text": "totaling approximately $675 million, were partially offset by lower sales volumes, negative currency", "bbox": [237.5, 1308.4, 1112.4, 1329.3]}, {"text": "effects of about $355 million, severance and related costs of $128 million, increased pension expense of", "bbox": [237.5, 1333.4, 1112.5, 1354.3]}, {"text": "about $155 million, higher operating costs and increased strategic marketing spending. Operating profit", "bbox": [237.5, 1358.4, 1112.3, 1379.3]}, {"text": "as a percent of net sales increased to 14.8 percent from 13.1 percent in 2008. Charges in 2008 of", "bbox": [237.5, 1383.4, 1112.5, 1404.3]}, {"text": "$60 million for strategic cost reductions, which were a part of a multi-year plan completed in 2008 to", "bbox": [237.5, 1408.4, 1112.5, 1429.3]}, {"text": "improve our competitive position, are not included in the results of the business segments.", "bbox": [237.5, 1433.4, 990.6, 1454.3]}, {"text": "21", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}